headline: Cleric Launches the First Self-Learning AI SRE
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, December 09, 2025--Cleric launches the first AI SRE that continuously learns from every incident so software engineers can focus on building instead of firefighting.

headline: Is Datadog Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Datadog has trailed the Nasdaq Composite over the past year, yet analysts remain highly confident in the company’s long-term growth outlook.

headline: RBC sees software M&A heating up. Who’s next in line?
summary: Investing.com -- Dealmaking in the software sector is accelerating into year-end, with RBC Capital Markets pointing to a sharp pickup in activity and a growing list of potential targets as strategic buyers and private equity firms scour the market.
